OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779649870
OL,3,CPM calls for Strait of Hormuz to open
OL,4,Cas US-Iran deal appears to draw closer
OL,6,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer has said
OL,7,Fthe Strait of Hormuz must be reopened
OL,8,Fwith "unconditional and unrestricted"
OL,9,Faccess for shipping, as a US-Iran deal
OL,10,Fappeared to be drawing closer.
OL,12,FUS President Donald Trump has said a
OL,13,Fdeal with Iran, which would include
OL,14,Fopening the strait, a vital oil and
OL,15,Fgas shipping route, has been "largely
OL,16,Fnegotiated"
OL,18,FTrump said "final aspects of the deal"
OL,19,Fare currently being discussed.
OL,26,@wD@^OUxD@KO]zD@LOUzD@fO]
