OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779649870
OL,3,CPM calls for Strait of Hormuz to open
OL,4,Cas US-Iran deal appears to draw closer
OL,6,FStarmer said the UK would work with
OL,7,Fallies to "seize this moment" to help
OL,8,Fachieve a long-term solution in the
OL,9,FMiddle East.
OL,11,FStarmer said: "I welcome the progress
OL,12,Ftowards an agreement between the US
OL,13,Fand Iran.
OL,15,F"We need to see an agreement that
OL,16,Fbrings the conflict to an end and
OL,17,Freopens the Strait of Hormuz, with
OL,18,Funconditional and unrestricted freedom
OL,19,Fof navigation.
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@]O]sD@OOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779649870
OL,3,CPM calls for Strait of Hormuz to open
OL,4,Cas US-Iran deal appears to draw closer
OL,6,F"It's vital that Iran must never be
OL,7,Fallowed to develop a nuclear weapon.
OL,9,F"My Government will continue to do
OL,10,Feverything we can to protect British
OL,11,Fpeople from the impact of this
OL,12,Fconflict.
OL,14,F"We will work with our international
OL,15,Fpartners to seize this moment and
OL,16,Fachieve a long-term diplomatic
OL,17,Fsettlement."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@AOUyD@LO]
