CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779649870
OL,3,CPM calls for Strait of Hormuz to open
OL,4,Cas US-Iran deal appears to draw closer
OL,6,FThe UK has already announced that
OL,7,FRoyal Navy destroyer HMS Dragon has
OL,8,Fbeen sent to the Middle East to
OL,9,Fprepare for a possible international
OL,10,Fmission to safeguard shipping in the
OL,11,Fstrait if a peace deal is put in place.
OL,13,FThe strait has been effectively closed
OL,14,Fto most shipping by Iran since the US-
OL,15,FIsraeli bombing campaign began at the
OL,16,Fend of February.
OL,18,FThe closure of the strait, which
OL,19,Fnormally carries around 20% of global
OL,20,Foil and gas shipping, has driven up
OL,21,Fprices around the world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
