PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779649870
OL,3,CPM calls for Strait of Hormuz to open
OL,4,Cas US-Iran deal appears to draw closer
OL,6,FIn a post on his Truth Social
OL,7,Fplatform, Trump said: "Final aspects
OL,8,Fand details of the deal are currently
OL,9,Fbeing discussed, and will be announced
OL,10,Fshortly.
OL,12,F"In addition to many other elements of
OL,13,Fthe agreement, the Strait of Hormuz
OL,14,Fwill be opened."
